1
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:39,930
[NORTHWARD]

2
00:01:40,070 --> 00:01:41,930
[Episode 33]

3
00:01:50,530 --> 00:01:51,289
Where's Fenghua?

4
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:52,120
Sleeping in the bedroom.

5
00:01:52,150 --> 00:01:52,870
What's up with her?

6
00:01:52,890 --> 00:01:54,680
She's been feeling dizzy lately, sometimes even unable to stand.

7
00:01:54,710 --> 00:01:55,850
She might be worn out.

8
00:02:32,970 --> 00:02:33,970
Why are you here?

9
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:40,030
Let me take you to the hospital

10
00:02:40,430 --> 00:02:41,400
for a check-up.

11
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:44,810
I've already had one.

12
00:02:45,220 --> 00:02:46,290
Nothing serious.

13
00:02:47,430 --> 00:02:49,490
This constant dizziness is no small matter.

14
00:02:49,630 --> 00:02:51,220
Granny Ma used to have the same symptom.

15
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:55,680
I'm still young. How can you compare me to her?

16
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:58,530
Do you think someone at my age could have a stroke?

17
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,740
Just mind your own business.

18
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:05,400
I'll handle my own affairs.

19
00:03:05,910 --> 00:03:07,180
Just stay out of this.

20
00:03:11,010 --> 00:03:12,100
So what did you do?

21
00:03:13,570 --> 00:03:15,090
I've been busy all day,

22
00:03:15,530 --> 00:03:17,170
getting He a death certificate

23
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,710
and contacting a funeral parlor.

24
00:03:19,390 --> 00:03:21,390
Has Bee made any effort at all?

25
00:03:21,870 --> 00:03:23,360
Did it occur to you that, given his family's situation,

26
00:03:23,380 --> 00:03:24,980
it was even uneasy for them to arrange a funeral?

27
00:03:25,340 --> 00:03:27,810
Have you thought about giving He some final dignity?

28
00:03:30,970 --> 00:03:33,970
Handle your own affairs? How dare you say that?

29
00:03:43,380 --> 00:03:45,120
Yes, you're right.

30
00:03:47,450 --> 00:03:48,970
I didn't take them into account.

31
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:50,880
I only

32
00:03:52,260 --> 00:03:54,700
thought about getting more compensation for them.

33
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:59,190
I wasn't thoughtful enough.

34
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:01,530
I was wrong.

35
00:04:09,550 --> 00:04:10,840
I'm really sorry.

36
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:14,430
I'll listen to your advice.

37
00:04:15,890 --> 00:04:16,829
And I'll adapt.

38
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:19,920
You should also listen to my suggestion.

39
00:04:21,890 --> 00:04:22,940
What suggestion?

40
00:04:23,300 --> 00:04:24,300
Go for a medical check-up.

41
00:04:25,660 --> 00:04:26,660
Let's go to Xiehe Hospital

42
00:04:26,900 --> 00:04:28,250
for the best doctor.

43
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,830
Not now.

44
00:04:30,860 --> 00:04:32,630
Not before I wrap these things up.

45
00:04:32,650 --> 00:04:34,250
How much compensation can there be?

46
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:45,270
We're still working on it.

47
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:47,820
We hope...

48
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:52,480
We hope to get the highest level.

49
00:04:58,960 --> 00:05:00,190
A new day has begun.

50
00:05:00,220 --> 00:05:01,680
Be careful on the way, everyone!

51
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,600
Okay!

52
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,090
Follow the traffic rules!

53
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:04,920
Okay!

54
00:05:04,940 --> 00:05:06,000
Come on! Our slogan!

55
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:07,920
Bee! Bee!

56
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:09,390
Have a safe trip!

57
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:10,070
Let's go!

58
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:10,890
Go!

59
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,530
Listen to me.

60
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,720
That guy doesn't look like a good person!

61
00:05:25,750 --> 00:05:26,390
Mom,

62
00:05:26,390 --> 00:05:27,800
if the people from Yuntu are not good,

63
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,560
are the people from Bee any better?

64
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:31,750
How can you believe those people will settle it?

65
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:34,270
Haven't you seen the attitude of their company?

66
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:35,480
If they had any conscience,

67
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:36,720
would Tianming have had an accident?

68
00:05:37,430 --> 00:05:38,840
But I think

69
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,360
something's fishy about this matter.

70
00:05:40,390 --> 00:05:42,190
I don't care if there's anything fishy!

71
00:05:42,220 --> 00:05:43,750
You really can't go!

72
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:44,630
Listen to me, okay?

73
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:46,560
You promised Ms. Xia before.

74
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,750
You're breaking your promise if you go now.

75
00:05:48,770 --> 00:05:50,360
What did I promise her?

76
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:52,510
She said Xie Wanghe would get us compensation.

77
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:53,330
So where's the money?

78
00:05:53,350 --> 00:05:54,360
I can't see them right now,

79
00:05:54,390 --> 00:05:55,800
let alone the money!

80
00:05:55,820 --> 00:05:57,610
They're obviously going back on their words!

81
00:05:58,070 --> 00:05:58,830
What's going on?

82
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:01,950
Please talk her out of it.

83
00:06:01,970 --> 00:06:04,310
Let her stop messing around.

84
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:05,390
What does she want to do?

85
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:08,000
Someone came here

86
00:06:08,020 --> 00:06:09,950
and said they'd pay for our lawsuit

87
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:12,390
to claim compensation from Bee.

88
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:14,390
They also talked about holding a press conference

89
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:16,430
to make this issue blow up completely!

90
00:06:16,460 --> 00:06:17,460
Who said that?

91
00:06:18,290 --> 00:06:20,340
I suspect it was someone from Yuntu.

92
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,630
Yuntu?

93
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,860
I have his business card.

94
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:25,600
What are you doing?

95
00:06:25,660 --> 00:06:27,250
They're genuinely trying to help us.

96
00:06:27,280 --> 00:06:29,190
They've put in money, effort, and labor.

97
00:06:29,210 --> 00:06:30,700
Don't be ungrateful.

98
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,530
You believe that?

99
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,560
This is apparently a business battle.

100
00:06:34,580 --> 00:06:35,690
They want to use this case

101
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,420
to completely ruin Bee's reputation.

102
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:38,950
I don't care about their intentions.

103
00:06:38,980 --> 00:06:41,270
I only know they've paid real money.

104
00:06:42,820 --> 00:06:43,690
How much?

105
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,440
How much money?

106
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,920
300,000.

107
00:06:50,290 --> 00:06:51,860
I've received the transfer on my card.

108
00:06:52,690 --> 00:06:53,800
No matter what,

109
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:56,140
they transferred the money before even signing an agreement.

110
00:06:56,260 --> 00:06:57,190
What about you guys?

111
00:06:57,220 --> 00:06:58,370
What have you done?

112
00:06:58,470 --> 00:07:00,370
Can you shut up?

113
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:02,400
Ms. Xia is doing this for our own good.

114
00:07:02,420 --> 00:07:03,930
You should be grateful!

115
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:06,180
Anyone can say nice things.

116
00:07:06,530 --> 00:07:08,240
If she really cares about us,

117
00:07:08,260 --> 00:07:09,700
she should give us money.

118
00:07:09,730 --> 00:07:10,900
I only believe in money now.

119
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:15,270
Return the money you received.

120
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:16,640
Just 300,000 yuan, right?

121
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:17,350
I'll pay it.

122
00:07:19,180 --> 00:07:20,800
Where can you get that money?

123
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:22,030
Don't worry about that.

124
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:23,530
Just return the money right away.

125
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,710
I'll cover the losses.

126
00:07:25,170 --> 00:07:28,210
Also, please give me one more day.

127
00:07:28,550 --> 00:07:30,030
I'll make sure Wanghe

128
00:07:30,070 --> 00:07:31,930
resolves the compensation issue as soon as possible.

129
00:07:33,820 --> 00:07:34,540
Return it.

130
00:07:35,250 --> 00:07:36,070
Go return it now.

131
00:07:44,330 --> 00:07:45,090
Hello.

132
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,930
Ms. Xia, what's the matter?

133
00:07:47,570 --> 00:07:49,300
Are you available tomorrow morning?

134
00:07:49,330 --> 00:07:50,940
I'd like to discuss something with you.

135
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,570
Can't we talk about it on the phone?

136
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:54,950
It's good news.

137
00:07:54,970 --> 00:07:55,820
Let's talk when we meet.

138
00:07:56,450 --> 00:07:57,450
See you tomorrow at 10 AM.

139
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,670
I'll send you the address.

140
00:07:58,690 --> 00:07:59,380
Alright.

141
00:07:59,740 --> 00:08:01,130
Send it to my phone.

142
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,870
Okay, bye-bye.

143
00:08:42,220 --> 00:08:42,980
Mr. Meng.

144
00:08:44,470 --> 00:08:47,130
Now that your meeting is over, can we talk?

145
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:56,790
Go ahead.

146
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,760
How much compensation do you expect the company to pay?

147
00:08:59,610 --> 00:09:01,880
The more, the better, of course.

148
00:09:02,660 --> 00:09:04,300
You know He's family situation.

149
00:09:04,330 --> 00:09:06,490
I know! And I feel sorry for them too!

150
00:09:07,330 --> 00:09:09,980
But I don't want the company to pay a penny.

151
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,200
What?

152
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,550
We can pay as much as they want personally,

153
00:09:12,550 --> 00:09:14,630
but the company can't. Do you understand?

154
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:25,030
Xie Wanghe,

155
00:09:25,570 --> 00:09:27,810
the company is about to go public.

156
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:30,410
We're facing millions of delivery riders.

157
00:09:30,510 --> 00:09:32,400
Any excessive compensation,

158
00:09:32,430 --> 00:09:33,510
if set as a precedent,

159
00:09:33,540 --> 00:09:35,780
will become a noose around our necks.

160
00:09:36,470 --> 00:09:38,650
It's a domino effect.

161
00:09:42,020 --> 00:09:44,560
Meng, how can you be so cold-blooded?

162
00:09:44,610 --> 00:09:45,890
For a businessman,

163
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:47,570
"cold-blooded" isn't a negative term.

164
00:09:47,590 --> 00:09:49,650
He died in the line of duty.

165
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:51,590
With the family's pillar gone,

166
00:09:51,620 --> 00:09:53,800
it's hard for the widow and orphan to survive!

167
00:09:56,890 --> 00:09:58,900
The company will definitely go public next year.

168
00:09:58,930 --> 00:10:00,650
Have you calculated your own net worth?

169
00:10:01,490 --> 00:10:02,780
If you really can't bear to see it,

170
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:04,240
just pay out of your own pocket.

171
00:10:04,270 --> 00:10:06,190
Pay for peace of mind.

172
00:10:35,860 --> 00:10:36,610
[Slow Down]

173
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,110
[Slow Down]

174
00:10:38,110 --> 00:10:40,570
[Fenghua Express]

175
00:10:47,830 --> 00:10:49,710
How's it going? Any updates?

176
00:11:14,210 --> 00:11:17,910
[Xie Wanghe] [August 20, 2015]

177
00:11:18,610 --> 00:11:19,730
Do you have any inkpad?

178
00:11:35,600 --> 00:11:38,480
My son, I miss you.

179
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:43,150
My son...

180
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:50,190
I miss you so much...

181
00:11:54,700 --> 00:11:56,460
My son...

182
00:11:58,900 --> 00:12:01,460
I miss you.

183
00:12:05,950 --> 00:12:07,520
Son...

184
00:12:11,710 --> 00:12:12,750
Ma'am,

185
00:12:13,470 --> 00:12:14,350
Mrs. He,

186
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:16,230
I know

187
00:12:17,340 --> 00:12:18,570
I bear the main responsibility

188
00:12:19,140 --> 00:12:20,750
for Tianming's accident

189
00:12:21,850 --> 00:12:23,610
I'm not asking for your forgiveness,

190
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:27,900
but I will do what I should.

191
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,740
I'll pay off your mortgage

192
00:12:32,420 --> 00:12:33,430
for the house,

193
00:12:33,710 --> 00:12:35,010
all at once.

194
00:12:35,580 --> 00:12:38,680
And also for the babies Mrs. He's carrying,

195
00:12:38,990 --> 00:12:42,140
I'll also sponsor their tuition.

196
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:45,530
This is my letter of commitment.

197
00:12:49,140 --> 00:12:50,750
Just with a worthless piece of paper,

198
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:53,440
you want us to let go of Bee?

199
00:12:53,570 --> 00:12:54,970
Dream on!

200
00:12:56,270 --> 00:12:58,570
We won't let you go!

201
00:13:07,530 --> 00:13:08,240
Mrs. He,

202
00:13:09,740 --> 00:13:12,400
the company has already initiated the compensation process.

203
00:13:13,170 --> 00:13:14,420
There will be bereavement payments.

204
00:13:15,220 --> 00:13:16,420
This letter of commitment

205
00:13:17,550 --> 00:13:19,230
is my personal promise.

206
00:13:19,580 --> 00:13:21,170
If you don't trust it,

207
00:13:21,780 --> 00:13:23,990
you can have a lawyer notarize it.

208
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:27,020
You have my word.

209
00:13:27,640 --> 00:13:29,070
I'll definitely fulfill it.

210
00:13:40,370 --> 00:13:42,900
My poor son...

211
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:50,470
I miss you!

212
00:13:57,410 --> 00:13:59,880
My poor son...

213
00:14:21,740 --> 00:14:23,360
I feel something's off.

214
00:14:24,230 --> 00:14:25,710
A host of netizens are denouncing you

215
00:14:26,410 --> 00:14:27,700
with particularly harsh words.

216
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,280
Isn't that normal?

217
00:14:32,050 --> 00:14:33,240
I am responsible

218
00:14:33,980 --> 00:14:34,980
for He's death.

219
00:14:37,510 --> 00:14:38,420
But

220
00:14:39,490 --> 00:14:41,080
it feels like it's organized.

221
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:44,200
Too many newly registered users.

222
00:14:44,220 --> 00:14:45,420
I think

223
00:14:45,810 --> 00:14:47,970
someone must have organized an army of trolls.

224
00:14:47,990 --> 00:14:48,870
You mean Yuntu?

225
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:50,020
No matter who it is,

226
00:14:50,630 --> 00:14:51,750
if we don't handle it soon,

227
00:14:51,780 --> 00:14:53,420
things will surely get out of hand in the media.

228
00:15:02,790 --> 00:15:05,900
A-Actually, no one expected

229
00:15:05,930 --> 00:15:08,100
such extreme weather that day.

230
00:15:08,210 --> 00:15:10,280
We also lost one of our colleagues.

231
00:15:12,250 --> 00:15:14,750
The company didn't even have time to celebrate before...

232
00:15:14,750 --> 00:15:15,960
I see.

233
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,000
We're well aware

234
00:15:17,020 --> 00:15:18,670
of what you just said.

235
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:20,600
We just want to hear

236
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:21,840
what you know,

237
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,200
and also

238
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:25,050
the stuff we're interested in.

239
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:25,720
You get it, right?

240
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:27,850
Excuse me,

241
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:28,870
I need to use the restroom.

242
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:38,960
Li.

243
00:15:40,630 --> 00:15:41,350
Mr. Qiu.

244
00:15:44,530 --> 00:15:46,270
Let me show you something.

245
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,470
Take a closer look.

246
00:15:51,340 --> 00:15:56,800
[Xiangmanlou Restaurant] [July 10]

247
00:15:51,340 --> 00:15:56,800
[Business Trip in Guangzhou] [From July 1 to July 5]

248
00:15:51,340 --> 00:15:56,800
[Jiangpan Hotel] [June 29]

249
00:15:59,870 --> 00:16:00,480
Mr. Qiu...

250
00:16:00,510 --> 00:16:01,150
Mr. Qiu, I...

251
00:16:01,320 --> 00:16:02,080
Why so nervous?

252
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,480
Improper expense claims

253
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:07,550
are not rare in big companies like ours.

254
00:16:08,390 --> 00:16:09,330
These of yours

255
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:12,240
are very, very small amounts,

256
00:16:12,980 --> 00:16:15,020
not reaching the level of misappropriation.

257
00:16:15,630 --> 00:16:16,440
At most,

258
00:16:17,870 --> 00:16:19,090
you'll just be fired

259
00:16:19,320 --> 00:16:21,200
with a little stain left on your resume.

260
00:16:21,860 --> 00:16:22,800
-Mr. Qiu, I...
-Li,

261
00:16:23,480 --> 00:16:25,080
I remember you joined the company

262
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:28,440
about three years ago, right?

263
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:31,000
Yeah, three years ago.

264
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:33,080
When did you start working

265
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,440
as Mr. Xie's assistant?

266
00:16:36,180 --> 00:16:37,100
In the summer

267
00:16:38,050 --> 00:16:38,820
of last year.

268
00:16:39,270 --> 00:16:39,940
Well, then,

269
00:16:40,990 --> 00:16:42,770
Mr. Xie must treat you well, right?

270
00:16:43,750 --> 00:16:44,410
Yeah...

271
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:44,870
Not bad...

272
00:16:44,870 --> 00:16:46,070
Did he give you a raise?

273
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,160
Nope.

274
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:49,220
Then year-end bonus?

275
00:16:49,540 --> 00:16:50,230
Others

276
00:16:50,250 --> 00:16:51,410
get double pay at the end of the year.

277
00:16:51,670 --> 00:16:52,870
Given your relationship with him,

278
00:16:52,870 --> 00:16:54,450
you must get at least triple pay, right?

279
00:16:57,630 --> 00:16:58,440
Li,

280
00:16:59,510 --> 00:17:02,140
from the first day you joined the company three years ago,

281
00:17:03,260 --> 00:17:04,480
I could tell

282
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:06,480
that you were a loyal young man.

283
00:17:07,079 --> 00:17:08,880
But don't you think

284
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:11,160
it's too foolish to stick to this loyalty?

285
00:17:11,609 --> 00:17:12,410
As your senior,

286
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,750
I must tell you

