made him a scapegoat.

564
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:43,830
That must be the case.

565
00:31:43,830 --> 00:31:46,110
Yeah, Wanghe's been righteous and kind-hearted

566
00:31:46,110 --> 00:31:47,590
since he was a kid.

567
00:31:47,610 --> 00:31:49,200
He knows when to hold back

568
00:31:49,200 --> 00:31:50,820
instead of acting recklessly.

569
00:31:50,850 --> 00:31:52,680
-Exactly.
-He must have been wrongly accused!

570
00:31:52,700 --> 00:31:54,910
Yeah! He's such a good boy!

571
00:31:54,940 --> 00:31:56,490
It's not a big deal.

572
00:31:56,510 --> 00:31:58,230
After all, internet trends

573
00:31:58,310 --> 00:32:00,290
will die down in a few days.

574
00:32:00,320 --> 00:32:01,310
Or we can have him back

575
00:32:01,310 --> 00:32:02,810
to lay low for a while!

576
00:32:02,830 --> 00:32:05,370
The internet never forgets.

577
00:32:05,510 --> 00:32:07,100
With a record of this incident,

578
00:32:07,130 --> 00:32:09,030
it'll be hard for Wanghe to find a job again.

579
00:32:09,710 --> 00:32:10,920
Why bother finding a job?

580
00:32:10,950 --> 00:32:12,250
As quick-witted as Wanghe is,

581
00:32:12,280 --> 00:32:14,250
can't he come back to start a business on the Flower Street?

582
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:15,780
Let them all come back,

583
00:32:15,800 --> 00:32:16,630
like Fenghua

584
00:32:16,660 --> 00:32:17,510
and Haikuo!

585
00:32:17,530 --> 00:32:18,770
Doesn't Haikuo do programming?

586
00:32:18,800 --> 00:32:20,120
He can do this job anywhere!

587
00:32:20,150 --> 00:32:21,000
Let them join hands.

588
00:32:21,000 --> 00:32:22,430
I'm sure they'll succeed!

589
00:32:22,550 --> 00:32:24,360
Well said! I totally agree.

590
00:32:24,380 --> 00:32:26,380
Fenghua just said that the life in Beijing had worn her out.

591
00:32:26,410 --> 00:32:27,720
Ask them all to come back.

592
00:32:27,750 --> 00:32:28,950
Beijing may be great,

593
00:32:29,030 --> 00:32:30,550
but it can't beat home sweet home.

594
00:32:30,550 --> 00:32:32,140
What are you talking about?

595
00:32:32,160 --> 00:32:33,270
Beijing is still better.

596
00:32:33,400 --> 00:32:34,270
It's the capital, after all!

597
00:32:34,270 --> 00:32:35,310
What's so good about Beijing?

598
00:32:35,310 --> 00:32:36,880
The high cost of living?

599
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:38,590
For a bowl of noodles with shredded eel,

600
00:32:38,590 --> 00:32:39,640
h-how much does it cost here?

601
00:32:39,680 --> 00:32:40,310
And how much is it in Beijing?

602
00:32:40,310 --> 00:32:40,960
How much?

603
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:42,790
Well, Mr. Zhou usually doesn't even charge us.

604
00:32:42,830 --> 00:32:43,750
Right?

605
00:32:43,750 --> 00:32:45,550
You guys go on. I'll go make you some noodles.

606
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:47,570
That's easy to say!

607
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:48,790
But if you want them to come back and start a business,

608
00:32:48,790 --> 00:32:50,290
will you provide the startup funds?

609
00:32:50,580 --> 00:32:52,240
So why do you want them to come back?

610
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:53,790
-We can look after them if they're back!
-Yeah!

611
00:32:53,810 --> 00:32:55,290
Does that really help?

612
00:32:55,310 --> 00:32:56,680
What do they do?

613
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:58,000
Well, then just look at the status quo!

614
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:59,680
No one is developing anything anymore.

615
00:33:00,610 --> 00:33:02,420
I think our hometown is quite good.

616
00:33:02,510 --> 00:33:03,700
A place with complete facilities,

617
00:33:03,720 --> 00:33:05,040
lush mountains,

618
00:33:05,110 --> 00:33:07,640
crystal-clear waters, skyscrapers, and everything we need.

619
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:09,680
On our Flower Street, we have tofu pudding

620
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:11,550
and noodles early in the morning, shredded eel at noon.

621
00:33:11,550 --> 00:33:13,030
Isn't it wonderful enough?

622
00:33:13,030 --> 00:33:14,200
Look at Wanghe...

623
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:20,530
[Fenghua Express]

624
00:33:25,030 --> 00:33:26,550
Don't worry, I'm fine.

625
00:33:30,840 --> 00:33:31,790
Then I'll go now.

626
00:33:41,150 --> 00:33:41,950
Fenghua,

627
00:33:44,640 --> 00:33:45,720
don't make any other plans

628
00:33:45,740 --> 00:33:46,780
for this weekend,

629
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:48,430
Why?

630
00:33:48,450 --> 00:33:49,870
As I said before,

631
00:33:49,890 --> 00:33:51,060
you should go to Xiehe Hospital

632
00:33:51,090 --> 00:33:52,480
for a full medical check-up.

633
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:56,320
And as I said before, it's unnecessary.

634
00:33:57,530 --> 00:33:59,560
If you don't go, I'll tell your mom.

635
00:34:00,610 --> 00:34:01,830
Whatever.

636
00:34:01,460 --> 00:34:06,310
[Slow Down]

637
00:34:02,780 --> 00:34:04,730
Please, I'm begging you.

638
00:34:04,770 --> 00:34:06,490
You really don't look well lately.

639
00:34:06,510 --> 00:34:07,640
No sparkling eyes.

640
00:34:08,270 --> 00:34:10,139
Even your voice is weak when you speak.

641
00:34:10,159 --> 00:34:11,429
It's heartbreaking to hear.

642
00:34:12,880 --> 00:34:14,380
I'm just jaded.

643
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:16,400
Can you stop pestering me?

644
00:34:16,440 --> 00:34:17,139
It's just one day.

645
00:34:17,159 --> 00:34:18,280
It's just one day.

646
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:20,440
I'm begging you.

647
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:23,920
After the check-up,

648
00:34:23,960 --> 00:34:25,340
we can go shopping together.

649
00:34:25,370 --> 00:34:27,440
I'll buy you anything you want, okay?

650
00:34:29,620 --> 00:34:30,449
Which day?

651
00:34:30,469 --> 00:34:31,800
Saturday or Sunday, whichever is okay

652
00:34:31,830 --> 00:34:33,040
for you.

653
00:34:34,090 --> 00:34:35,199
Alright.

654
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:37,440
Just wait for my message.

655
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:39,550
Take care.

656
00:34:42,429 --> 00:34:43,670
Don't forget.

657
00:34:43,719 --> 00:34:45,190
I'll come and pick you up then.

658
00:34:59,230 --> 00:35:00,420
Get some rest early.

659
00:36:45,280 --> 00:36:45,880
What do you think

660
00:36:45,920 --> 00:36:47,080
of this place I found?

661
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:48,940
A nice shelter from wind and rain.

662
00:36:49,970 --> 00:36:51,940
In the future, this whole area

663
00:36:51,960 --> 00:36:55,030
will be filled with shelves for parcels.

664
00:36:55,190 --> 00:36:57,420
As for the sofa and coffee table

665
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:58,880
from your station,

666
00:36:59,100 --> 00:37:00,290
I'll put them right here,

667
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:03,240
making this into an employee rest area.

668
00:37:03,700 --> 00:37:04,880
Am I thoughtful?

669
00:37:05,580 --> 00:37:06,690
That's really nice.

670
00:37:06,940 --> 00:37:07,880
Sun,

671
00:37:08,030 --> 00:37:09,470
it's a brilliant idea to let you

672
00:37:09,520 --> 00:37:10,700
take over the station.

673
00:37:13,950 --> 00:37:15,990
Have you made up your mind?

674
00:37:16,130 --> 00:37:17,200
Are you really quitting?

675
00:37:18,240 --> 00:37:19,460
I'm tired of it.

676
00:37:20,010 --> 00:37:22,080
Remember to treat them well.

677
00:37:22,260 --> 00:37:23,920
If anyone comes to complain to me,

678
00:37:23,950 --> 00:37:25,120
I'll hold you accountable.

679
00:37:25,140 --> 00:37:26,450
C'mon,

680
00:37:26,650 --> 00:37:28,020
just rest assured.

681
00:37:28,150 --> 00:37:30,150
They'll be my staff from now on.

682
00:37:30,180 --> 00:37:31,450
I'll take care of them.

683
00:37:32,700 --> 00:37:33,830
That's a deal.

684
00:37:34,570 --> 00:37:35,180
Okay!

685
00:37:36,830 --> 00:37:38,120
I believe

686
00:37:38,150 --> 00:37:40,920
you've all heard about our station's merging

687
00:37:40,940 --> 00:37:42,640
with Mr. Sun's station.

688
00:37:42,670 --> 00:37:44,710
It's great to have two strong parties join forces.

689
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:49,660
From now on, for all the steps like sorting, delivery, signing, to after-sales service,

690
00:37:49,810 --> 00:37:53,020
you should follow the standards and requirements

691
00:37:53,220 --> 00:37:54,410
stated in this manual.

692
00:37:55,500 --> 00:37:57,210
So who do we listen to from now on?

693
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:04,670
After merging, you'll be one big family.

694
00:38:05,410 --> 00:38:07,410
I've already talked to Mr. Sun.

695
00:38:07,590 --> 00:38:09,250
You should all follow his lead from now on.

696
00:38:11,150 --> 00:38:12,110
What does that mean?

697
00:38:12,110 --> 00:38:13,110
After the merger, you...

698
00:38:13,140 --> 00:38:14,690
You won't be in charge anymore?

699
00:38:16,050 --> 00:38:17,100
I should step down.

700
00:38:18,770 --> 00:38:21,460
Mr. Sun will be in charge from now on.

701
00:38:22,980 --> 00:38:24,670
Then we're done for...

702
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:27,480
We are going to suffer!

703
00:38:30,650 --> 00:38:32,020
Don't worry, everyone.

704
00:38:32,990 --> 00:38:36,030
I've negotiated all the terms before the merger.

705
00:38:36,270 --> 00:38:38,500
I've secured all your benefits

706
00:38:38,520 --> 00:38:39,600
and needs,

707
00:38:41,220 --> 00:38:42,780
like social insurance, housing fund,

708
00:38:42,930 --> 00:38:44,370
paid annual leave,

709
00:38:44,710 --> 00:38:47,270
and also year-end performance evaluations and awards.

710
00:38:47,750 --> 00:38:49,590
As long as you work diligently,

711
00:38:49,610 --> 00:38:51,860
your benefits won't be any less than those of big companies.

712
00:39:00,070 --> 00:39:02,630
It's okay if you don't wanna stay.

713
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:05,340
I still have some connections with HQ.

714
00:39:05,810 --> 00:39:07,050
if you need,

715
00:39:07,070 --> 00:39:08,530
I can help you negotiate it

716
00:39:08,630 --> 00:39:10,380
and get you into a nearby parcel delivery station.

717
00:39:11,290 --> 00:39:12,850
I still say the same thing.

718
00:39:13,720 --> 00:39:15,130
Take your time to make money.

719
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:18,910
I hope you all take care of yourselves.

720
00:39:19,790 --> 00:39:20,980
Please, please,

721
00:39:21,240 --> 00:39:22,310
be careful and stay safe.

722
00:39:23,540 --> 00:39:25,220
I wish each and every one of you

723
00:39:25,730 --> 00:39:28,220
a bright and wonderful future.

724
00:39:47,710 --> 00:39:48,460
Wanghe?

725
00:39:48,490 --> 00:39:49,410
Wanghe!

726
00:39:49,430 --> 00:39:50,550
Wanghe.

727
00:39:50,550 --> 00:39:51,150
Wake up, wake up.

728
00:39:51,150 --> 00:39:52,320
Come on, Wanghe.

729
00:39:53,030 --> 00:39:55,080
Get up! Fenghua has left!

730
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:56,230
Where did she go?

731
00:39:56,230 --> 00:39:56,880
Home.

732
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:58,550
She's not coming back to Beijing after leaving.

733
00:39:58,680 --> 00:39:59,340
What?

734
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:01,000
I wrote a time management software for her

735
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:01,880
and asked her to find someone to test it.

736
00:40:01,920 --> 00:40:03,370
She told me to send it to Mr. Sun as she had quit

737
00:40:03,400 --> 00:40:05,230
and wouldn't be managing that business anymore.

738
00:40:06,670 --> 00:40:08,010
Hey, wait for me.

