♫Blowing through the forest and the city♫

742
00:40:28,620 --> 00:40:31,400
♫Blowing through your face♫

743
00:40:32,900 --> 00:40:35,930
♫And my heart♫

744
00:40:35,360 --> 00:40:36,200
Did you get through to her?

745
00:40:36,900 --> 00:40:39,560
♫The wind blows gently♫

746
00:40:37,110 --> 00:40:38,730
