00:41:01,680 --> 00:41:03,330
♫I love you♫

756
00:41:03,770 --> 00:41:07,750
♫In dreams or in the south♫

757
00:41:05,610 --> 00:41:06,810
Take care, Fenghua.

758
00:41:07,150 --> 00:41:08,800
Take care, Fenghua!

