00:41:48,270 --> 00:41:54,470
[Fenghua Express]

764
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:53,960
♫That's me♫

765
00:41:54,600 --> 00:41:55,540
Put them down!

766
00:41:54,740 --> 00:42:00,050
♫Missing you deeply again♫

