774
00:42:14,640 --> 00:42:16,100
Ms. Xia has quit!

775
00:42:16,120 --> 00:42:17,780
We used to work for the same company.

776
00:42:17,800 --> 00:42:19,950
I've taken over this station.

777
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:21,960
No way!

778
00:42:22,030 --> 00:42:23,240
Calm down, please.

779
00:42:23,550 --> 00:42:25,800
Ms. Xia and I made this decision together.

780
00:42:25,930 --> 00:42:26,930
Just a few days ago,

781
00:42:26,960 --> 00:42:29,540
we went to inspect a factory.

782
00:42:29,940 --> 00:42:31,500
I'm quite touched by this.

783
00:42:31,710 --> 00:42:33,550
If she had stayed

784
00:42:33,570 --> 00:42:35,900
to work here, things would have turned out even better!

785
00:43:02,550 --> 00:43:03,700
So she really left, huh?

